WEBVTT

00:00.067 --> 00:02.140
<i>Previously on
"dead of summer"...</i>

00:02.170 --> 00:03.675
Margot Tate.

00:03.705 --> 00:05.295
Maybe we can be friends.

00:05.499 --> 00:06.992
Love those
ill-fitting Jordaches,

00:07.022 --> 00:08.066
by the way.

00:08.101 --> 00:09.356
Wait, Margot!

00:13.285 --> 00:14.587
There's more things coming.

00:14.617 --> 00:15.908
Maybe you didn't save
the world...

00:15.938 --> 00:18.441
But you might just be able
to save these kids.

00:19.179 --> 00:22.249
Find Amy.
The demon lives within her.

00:22.279 --> 00:23.451
Holyoke told
me and Jessie...

00:23.481 --> 00:24.987
To come save you.
I know.

00:25.519 --> 00:26.656
No!

00:27.454 --> 00:28.686
No!

00:32.787 --> 00:34.655
Aah!
Let go of me!

00:34.685 --> 00:35.931
You know where to go!

00:36.196 --> 00:38.740
I have to get the kids
out of here.

00:38.770 --> 00:39.820
Right now.

00:41.807 --> 00:44.649
Let us... begin.

