01:04.424 --> 01:05.361
Need a lift?

01:05.492 --> 01:08.635
You know
how to get to camp stillwater?

01:08.765 --> 01:10.947
I'm worried
about a friend of mine.

01:11.662 --> 01:13.063
Hop in.

01:22.848 --> 01:25.743
Please, you guys,
let me go.

01:26.452 --> 01:28.843
I didn't mean to hurt him.

01:30.444 --> 01:33.601
Joel, he was...
He was one of us.

01:35.338 --> 01:36.856
Sounds like her.

01:37.490 --> 01:41.226
The demon
is a master of deception.

01:47.716 --> 01:49.114
Open it.

02:07.380 --> 02:09.038
What kind of exorcism
is this?

02:09.169 --> 02:10.596
It's not an exorcism.

02:11.003 --> 02:12.792
It's a purification.

02:13.556 --> 02:17.134
That's the last pure water that
exists from lake stillwater,

02:17.264 --> 02:20.470
and it will save
Amy's soul.

02:21.496 --> 02:23.345
That's why Malphas
chose her.

02:24.212 --> 02:25.910
Because she was pure.

02:26.434 --> 02:30.463
Others have come before,
hoping to summon the demon,

02:30.593 --> 02:33.404
but no vessel has ever been
accepted until hers.

02:33.534 --> 02:39.422
She has made Malphas
more powerful than ever.

02:39.909 --> 02:42.453
And that strength
has left me weakened.

02:42.688 --> 02:45.922
Now I must lead the purification
myself.

02:46.052 --> 02:47.962
Defeating Malphas
is too important.

02:48.092 --> 02:53.194
It will require every bit
of my strength... and yours.

03:10.771 --> 03:12.401
<i>I call back seat!</i>

03:18.809 --> 03:20.256
We're ready.

03:20.919 --> 03:22.281
You all right?

03:23.273 --> 03:25.825
I never imagined
this is how I would say goodbye.

03:25.955 --> 03:27.240
You think they'll be okay?

03:27.370 --> 03:29.065
I hope so.

03:32.121 --> 03:33.477
Okay.

03:48.694 --> 03:52.815
<font color=#ff00ff>* dead of summer *</font>
<font color=#00ff00>Season 01 Episode 09 </font>
<font color=#ffff00>"Home Sweet Home"</font>
